Cytoskeleton Club meets once a month for informal talks. This is not a private club. Talks are open to everyone, so come along!
Cytoskeleton Club

First Wednesday of each month, 2pm (two 20-minute talks or one 40-minute talk)
Organizers: Reem Hakeem, Zayna King, and Laura McCormick




Call for Speakers! We have available slots for speakers in November and December. If you are interested in sharing your story and getting feedback from the community, email us to arrange a talk.
